<h2> <span class="mw-headline" id="Design_and_Construction_details">Design and Construction details</span></h2>
<table class="wikitable" style="float:right; margin: 1em auto 1em auto; text-align:center">
<caption>Sizes of the National Flag</caption>
<tr>
<th>Flag size<sup id="cite_ref-NIC_4-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-NIC-4"><span>[</span>3<span>]</span></a></sup></th>
<th>Length and width (<a href="Millimetres" title="Millimetres" class="mw-redirect">mm</a>)</th>
<th>Size of Ashoka Chakra (<a href="Millimetres" title="Millimetres" class="mw-redirect">mm</a>) <sup id="cite_ref-IS11968_5-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-IS11968-5"><span>[</span>4<span>]</span></a></sup></th>
</tr>
