<li><span class="citation Journal" id="CITEREFJha2008">Jha, Sadan (25 October 2008). "The Indian National Flag as a site of daily plebiscite". <i>Economic and political weekly</i>: 102–111. <a href="International_Standard_Serial_Number" title="International Standard Serial Number">ISSN</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.worldcat.org/issn/0012-9976">0012-9976</a>. <a href="OCLC" title="OCLC">OCLC</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.worldcat.org/oclc/1567377">1567377</a></span>.</li>
<li><span class="citation web"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.bis.org.in/sf/pow/txd.pdf">"Indian Standards"</a> (PDF). <i>Bureau of Indian Standards</i><span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://www.bis.org.in/sf/pow/txd.pdf">http://www.bis.org.in/sf/pow/txd.pdf</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved 1 July 2005</span>.</span></li>
<li><span class="citation web"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.crwflags.com/fotw/flags/in.html">"India"</a>. <i><a href="Flags_of_the_World" title="Flags of the World">Flags of the World</a></i><span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://www.crwflags.com/fotw/flags/in.html">http://www.crwflags.com/fotw/flags/in.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved 30 June 2005</span>.</span></li>
<li><span class="citation web"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.crwflags.com/fotw/flags/in-hist.html">"India: Historical Flags"</a>. <i>Flags of the World</i><span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://www.crwflags.com/fotw/flags/in-hist.html">http://www.crwflags.com/fotw/flags/in-hist.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved 30 June 2005</span>.</span></li>
